----------Instructions---------

1. Katevaste to Autohotkey kai to compiler SciTE4AutoHotkey

2. Mporeite na deite mesa apo to Github ton kodika episis.

3. Dhmiourgiste ena fakelo mesa ston ipologisti sas. ( den exei simasia pou tha einai )

3. Dhmiourgiste mesa sto fakelo pou molis dimiourgisate, enan allo fakelo
   me onoma "assets" (To onoma ine poli simantiko kai xoris ta "") kai valte mesa  to arxeio back.png & to arxio plat.ico

4. Otan katevasete to arxio .ahk kai exete stisei kai to compiler SciTE4AutoHotkey mporeite na kanete deksi click sto .afk arxeio
   kai na to kanete compile. Etsi tha dimiourgisete monoi sas to exe. 

5. Oi lithourgies tou programmatos anaferonte pano se ayto.
